Usage: create_stress_rule [-help] { {-layer <layerName> -spacing_table <spacing_table> [-chip_name <chipName>]} | [-reset ] }

-help                              # Prints out the command usage
-chip_name <chipName>              # chip names, { chipName }
                                   # (string, optional)
-layer <layerName>                 # stress layer name, { layerName }
                                   # (string, optional)
-reset                             # reset all stress rules (bool, optional)
-spacing_table <spacing_table>     # spacing table definition, { {x1 y1} {x2
                                   # y2} ...} (string, optional)